title: Update: Has Tommy Hit A Snag In His Weight Loss Journey?
description:
Tommy was very confident that he could make his ambitious goal of losing 80 pounds by Christmas work, and it seemed like he was on the right track! Now that we've hit October he'll give us an update on where he is on his journey.
